<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Cave_Automatic_Virtual_Environment&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Carolina_Cruz-Neira,_Daniel_J._Sandin,_Thomas_A._DeFanti,_Robert_V._Kenyon_and_John_C._Hart&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Carolina Cruz-Neira, Daniel J. Sandin, Thomas A. DeFanti, Robert V. Kenyon and John C. Hart (page does not exist)">Carolina Cruz-Neira, Daniel J. Sandin, Thomas A. DeFanti, Robert V. Kenyon and John C. Hart</a>. "The CAVE: Audio Visual Experience Automatic Virtual Environment", <i><a href="/wiki/Communications_of_the_ACM" title="Communications of the ACM">Communications of the ACM</a></i>, vol. 35(6), 1992, pp. 64-72. DOI:<a href="http://doi.acm.org/10.1145/129888.129892" class="external text" title="http://doi.acm.org/10.1145/129888.129892" rel="nofollow">10.1145/129888.129892</a></li>
